| Test suite | `/packages/openai/src/image/openai-image-model.test.ts` |
| Test fixtures | `/packages/openai/src/image/__fixtures__/openai-image.json` |
| Config type | `/packages/openai/src/openai-config.ts` |

This structure exemplifies a clean, modular provider implementation with clear separation of concerns: options/types, API schemas, model implementation, factory pattern, and comprehensive testing.

