I need to design a new fictional "PixelArt" AI provider for the Vercel AI SDK. This provider ONLY supports image generation (no text, no chat, no embeddings). I've thoroughly explored the codebase and have a complete understanding of the patterns. I'll lay out everything I know.

## Reference Implementation: LUMA provider (image-only)
The LUMA provider at `packages/luma/` is the simplest existing image-only provider and will be our primary reference.

### Files in the LUMA provider:
1. `package.json` - npm package config
2. `tsconfig.json` - extends `@vercel/ai-tsconfig/ts-library.json`, composite: true, references provider + provider-utils
3. `tsconfig.build.json` - extends tsconfig.json, disables composite
4. `tsup.config.ts` - build config (CJS + ESM, dts, sourcemap, __PACKAGE_VERSION__ define)
5. `vitest.node.config.js` - Node test config
6. `vitest.edge.config.js` - Edge runtime test config
7. `src/index.ts` - re-exports
8. `src/version.ts` - version string from build-time inject
9. `src/luma-provider.ts` - provider factory (createLuma, LumaProvider interface, LumaProviderSettings)
10. `src/luma-image-model.ts` - ImageModelV3 implementation
11. `src/luma-image-settings.ts` - model IDs and settings types

### Key Provider Patterns:
- Provider factory function: `createLuma(options: LumaProviderSettings = {}): LumaProvider`
- Default singleton export: `export const luma = createLuma()`
- Provider interface extends `ProviderV3` from `@ai-sdk/provider`
- Implements `image()` and `imageModel()` methods
- Throws `NoSuchModelError` for languageModel, embeddingModel, textEmbeddingModel
- Uses `loadApiKey()`, `withoutTrailingSlash()`, `withUserAgentSuffix()` from `@ai-sdk/provider-utils`
- Auth header pattern: `Authorization: Bearer ${loadApiKey(...)}`

### ImageModelV3 Interface (from @ai-sdk/provider):
```typescript
export type ImageModelV3 = {
  readonly specificationVersion: 'v3';
  readonly provider: string;
  readonly modelId: string;
  readonly maxImagesPerCall: number | undefined | GetMaxImagesPerCallFunction;
  doGenerate(options: ImageModelV3CallOptions): PromiseLike<{
    images: Array<string> | Array<Uint8Array>;
    warnings: Array<SharedV3Warning>;
    providerMetadata?: ImageModelV3ProviderMetadata;
    response: { timestamp: Date; modelId: string; headers: Record<string, string> | undefined; };
    usage?: ImageModelV3Usage;
  }>;
};
```

### ImageModelV3CallOptions:
```typescript
{
  prompt: string | undefined;
  n: number;
  size: `${number}x${number}` | undefined;
  aspectRatio: `${number}:${number}` | undefined;
  seed: number | undefined;
  files: ImageModelV3File[] | undefined;
  mask: ImageModelV3File | undefined;
  providerOptions: SharedV3ProviderOptions;
  abortSignal?: AbortSignal;
  headers?: Record<string, string | undefined>;
}
```

### Package.json pattern:
- name: `@ai-sdk/luma`
