Perfect! Now I have enough information. Let me create a comprehensive report for the user.

## Comprehensive Provider Implementation Study

I've thoroughly explored the Vercel AI SDK monorepo and analyzed how existing providers implement image generation. Here are my detailed findings:

### 1. Provider Package Structure

#### Directory Layout (e.g., packages/openai, packages/replicate, packages/fal):

```
packages/<provider>/
├── src/
│   ├── index.ts                           # Main export file
│   ├── <provider>-provider.ts             # Provider factory class
│   ├── <provider>-error.ts                # Error handling utilities
